name: inclCriteria
label: Inclusion criteria
description: Which criteria does the patient fullfill to be included in the registry?

name: ageDiagnosisKnown
label: Age at diagnosis (malignancy) available?
description: Is the age (years) at which the patient was diagnosed with this malignancy known?

name: ageDiagnosis
label: Age at diagnosis (malignancy)
description: At what age (years) was the patient diagnosed with this malignancy?

name: malignancyMorph
label: Malignancy morphology
description: What is the morphology of this malignancy?

name: ERreceptor
label: ER receptor status
description: What is the Estrogen receptor status of the breast cancer?

name: PRreceptor
label: PR receptor status
description: What is the Progesteron receptor status of the breast cancer?

name: Her2NeuReceptor
label: Her2Neu receptor status
description: What is the Her2Neu receptor status of the breast cancer?

name: laterality
label: Laterality
description: What is the laterality of the breast cancer?

name: diagnosisSource
label: Diagnosis source
description: What is the level of evidence for the diagnosis?

name: MMRtumour
label: MMR tumour diagnostics
description: Has IHC of the MMR protein or microsatellite instability analyses been performed?

name: MMR_IHC
label: MMR IHC status
description: What are the results of the IHC of the MMR proteins?
enumOptions: Test not performed, Normal, Loss of MLH1, Loss of PMS2 only, Loss of MSH2, Loss of MSH6 only, Other staining pattern, Unclear result, Unknown

name: MMR_MSA
label: MMR MSA status
description: What are the results of the MSA of the tumour DNA?
enumOptions: Test not performed, Normal (MSS or MSI-L), MSI-high, Unclear result, Unknown

name: MLH1promotor
label: MLH1 promoter hypermethylation or tumour BRAF V600E status
description: Has MLH1 promoter hypermethylation testing or tumour BRAF V600E mutation analyses been performed?
enumOptions: Test not performed, MLH1 promoter hypermethylation, No MLH1 promoter hypermethylation, Unclear MLH1 promoter methylation pattern, BRAF V600E tumour mutation present, No BRAF V600E tumour mutation present

name: somaticBialelicMMR
label: Somatic biallelic MMR mutation status
description: What are the results of the somatic MMR mutation analysis?
enumOptions: Test not performed, Biallelic somatic mutations present, No biallelic somatic mutations present
